'''Alfred Lothar Wegener''' ([[1 wamber]] [[1880]] - [[1 wamber]] [[1930]]) d [[amusnaw]], d [[Tasnallunt|amesnallun]] n [[Lalman]] illa izerrew (yeɣɣaṛ) [[takelsengamt]] d [[Tasnignewt|tesnignewt]] deg [[tizgelt n ugafa]]. Deg tudert-is, Wegener yettwassen s tigiyin-is deg tesnignewt akken iga d uzwir deg yinagiyen d inadiyen d tama n tizgelt n Ugafa, Maca seg imahilen yakk s wacu id yufrar d tisersi-ynes n [[Tazelma tamanẓawt|teẓri n tzelma tamanẓawt]] deg useggas n [[1912]]. Tiẓri ayyi tɣil d akken [[amenẓaw|imenẓawen]] llan ttwliwlen s ullan (ttḥerriwen cwiṭ cwiṭ) ɣef [[tagnit|tegnit]]. Dɣa tiẓri ayyi d tin yellan ur tettwaddeg ara (ur tettwaqbel ara) sɣur imusnawen d wammas ussnan alammi d [[tamrawt]] n [[tamrawt n 1950|smumraw (tixemsinin)]] n [[Tasut tis 20|tsut tis 20]] ass mi yewweṭ ad yaf aṭas n tegritin gar-asent [[Tadekrimzikt|Paleomagnetism]] yefkan asalel d tedhelt iddusin (ijehden) i teẓri n tezelma tamanẓawt i yuɣalen sin akin d azadur agejdan deg tmudmin titrarin i [[Tifilin titektuniyin|tfiliyin titektuniyin]] n tegnit.<ref name="earthy">{{amnir n wedlis|aneggar=Spaulding |amezwar=Nancy E. |amezwar2=Samuel N. |aneggar2=Namowitz |azwel=Earth Science |adeg=Boston |anefsar=McDougal Littell |aseggas=2005 |Uṭṭun ameslugen=0-618-11550-1}}</ref><ref>{{amnir n wedlis|aneggar1= McIntyre |amezwar1=Michael |aneggar2=Eilers |amezwar2=H. Peter |aneggar3= Mairs |amezwar3=John |azwel=Physical geography |aseggas= 1991 |anefsar= Wiley |adeg=New York  |uṭṭun ameslugen=0-471-62017-3 | tasna=273}}</ref>. Akken i yessaweṭ (Wegener) ad issegzu tumant n [[isigniwen imseflilliyen]].<ref>{{amnir n web |ameskar=Keesee, Bob |azwel=Noctilucent Clouds |akala=http://www.albany.edu/faculty/rgk/atm101/nlc.htm |anefsar=University of Albany |azmez n tuwwṭa=2008-10-19| akala n ufaylu = https://web.archive.org/web/20181111043723/https://www.albany.edu/faculty/rgk/atm101/nlc.htm | azmez n ufaylu = 11 wamber 2018 }}</ref>

